{"tid":1310492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後遇到便衣狗影人頭挑釁市民或者襲擊市民 一定要佢落單","createTime":"2019-07-12T16:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:08:37.000Z","uid":176442,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"434034603ea36277f9ef1b54171c79e8a358c184","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"唔好比其他狗埋到佢身<br />\n之後點各有各做<br />\n唔好再信香港警察會捉自己人"},{"pid":"05f1d84d19d643a87d26f9494d1856b498c8db1e","tid":1310492,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"告佢偷拍裙底"},{"pid":"bf69ca8f7cde6d425a4387577dd6f9908715e7ec","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"啱啱油塘單嘢<br />\n你比佢班狗同僚埋到身 只會保護佢走<br />\n<br />\n一定要令佢落單<br />\n然後各有各做（例如要佢道歉）<br />\n幾十人圍住佢班狗仔要入到救人都有困難"},{"pid":"d7cabcc3fac5370187b07061c6f6d161ce25e1d7","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"便衣狗<span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心</span>撞到其他人跌低受傷<br />\n我哋普通人一樣得"},{"pid":"0111dce065a8b21ec97918f523dcc26a3f0dfddd","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:52:21.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"0e69d444de4970419f5a68e63f2efe66572c4485","tid":1310492,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:53:29.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n<br />\n[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e8f4843b178992937e036e10d20ccc8f07e7d93","tid":1310492,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"各有各做各有各做"},{"pid":"8c29d24ba355a1796a67b58cfd7163e293fef276","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:11:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6863a64e7f3523bc89d77fffdbb8a8a69393621d","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:56:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今日有兩三單效法咗<br />\n<br />\n做得好撚好"},{"pid":"50e49efe8c3f3779832ea30e1e1cbf5d4784115e","tid":1310492,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"咩叫落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00723e299039eff779c677e0bdd5fe285bca7a24","tid":1310492,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"700963b82130433557147ba97b27b55786b11105","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50e49efe8c3f3779832ea30e1e1cbf5d4784115e","tid":1310492,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:57:59.000Z","msg":"咩叫落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:01:54.000Z","msg":"自行google"},{"pid":"bee0beaaefbf6c3d02121d14227b993123388f19","tid":1310492,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T15:12:46.0